<plot>This _Groundhog Day (1993)_ (qv) style comedy focuses on a midwife, finding herself living the same day over and over again. Anna, a single mother of two, works as a midwife and hasn't been on holidays for years. Unfortunately, when she wants to go to Italy, her neighbor asks her to accompany him and his pregnant girlfriend to the hospital. She helps giving birth to the baby reluctantly, and then grabs her children to start their journey. However, Anna wakes up in her own bed the next morning again...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041579</url></doc>
